trans-unit.source: AttunityAttunity CloudBeam provides an automated and optimized solution for loading data to SQL Data Warehouse. With a “click-to-load” design, it simplifies and accelerates both batch loading as well as incremental replication from many heterogeneous databases including SQL Server, Oracle, DB2, Sybase and mySQL.
